  - date: "2025-10-15"
    decision: "Optimization RLS Fix - Admins Can Now View All Recordings"
    status: "completed and deployed ‚úÖ"
    details: |
      üîê SECURITY FIX: RLS policies now allow admin users to view ALL optimization recordings

      ## Problem Reported by User:
      User (bruno@jumper.studio, admin) couldn't view optimization data at:
      http://localhost:8080/optimization/editor/306eb731-a5cc-45ea-83bb-91a07c6a9d54

      Page loaded but showed no transcript/context data.

      ## Investigation:
      1. ‚úÖ Recording exists in database (id: 306eb731-a5cc-45ea-83bb-91a07c6a9d54)
      2. ‚úÖ All statuses: completed (transcription, processing, analysis)
      3. ‚úÖ Transcript exists (447 chars full_text, 927 chars processed_text)
      4. ‚úÖ Context exists (1089 chars summary)
      5. ‚ùå Recording created by: claudio@jumper.studio
      6. ‚ùå User trying to access: bruno@jumper.studio (admin)

      ## Root Cause Discovery:
      RLS policies on optimization tables only allowed "Users can view their own":

      **Working (had admin policies):**
      - ‚úÖ j_hub_optimization_recordings: "Admins can view all recordings"
      - ‚úÖ j_hub_optimization_api_logs: "Admins can view all API logs"

      **Broken (missing admin policies):**
      - ‚ùå j_hub_optimization_transcripts: Only "Users can view their own transcripts"
      - ‚ùå j_hub_optimization_context: Only "Users can view their own context"

      ## Solution Implemented:
      Added 4 new RLS policies:

      ### j_hub_optimization_transcripts:
      - "Admins can view all transcripts" (SELECT)
      - "Admins can update all transcripts" (UPDATE)

      ### j_hub_optimization_context:
      - "Admins can view all context" (SELECT)
      - "Admins can update all context" (UPDATE)

      ## Deployment Process:
      1. ‚úÖ Created migration: 20251015000000_fix_optimization_rls_for_admins.sql
      2. ‚úÖ Applied locally via `supabase db reset`
      3. ‚úÖ Tested locally: bruno@jumper.studio viewing claudio@jumper.studio's recording
      4. ‚úÖ All 3 steps visible (transcript, processing, analysis)
      5. ‚úÖ Committed: e197cc5
      6. ‚úÖ Pushed to GitHub
      7. ‚úÖ Vercel auto-deployed frontend (v2.0.10)
      8. ‚úÖ User applied SQL manually in Supabase Dashboard (production)
      9. ‚úÖ Production tested and working

      ## Impact:
      - ‚úÖ Admins can now view/edit ALL optimization recordings
      - ‚úÖ Regular users still only see their own recordings
      - ‚úÖ Maintains security while enabling admin oversight
      - ‚úÖ Zero breaking changes for existing users

      ## Technical Details:
      Policy pattern used:
      ```sql
      USING (
        EXISTS (
          SELECT 1
          FROM j_hub_users
          WHERE j_hub_users.id = auth.uid()
          AND j_hub_users.role = 'admin'
        )
      )
      ```

      This checks if the current authenticated user has role='admin' in j_hub_users table.
    impact: "HIGH - Critical fix for admin user experience in optimization system"
